    "attributes": {
        "action": "Provide compensation for people who lost money on Portuguese holidays in June",
        "additional_details": "Thousands of people have lost deposits or 100% of their money due to government misguidance .This also includes covid tests paid for and transfers.\r\nSome people have not been given the option to change the booking and others have had to fly back earlier than planned.\r\n\r\nThe government said green for go and now we are given a maximum of 5 days to reorganise plans. ",
        "background": "The Government must compensate people who lost money when Portugal went from Green to Amber on the travel list in June 2021",
